title: The Syndicate - COMPLETE SERIES - (Season 1, 2, 3)
description: In each of the 3 seasons a different group of individuals regularly buy lottery tickets together (as a syndicate) and events and life are far from what each person imagined after their syndicate hits the jackpot:  With the millions comes many problems, dramas, and conflicts among the members of the syndicate, some who were cut out of the winnings, friends, co-workers and family members
